            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While your fish is cooking, slice your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Remove the base of your <strong>lettuce</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong> and cut away the core, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> from the stem until you are left with a pile of leaves</p><p>Set 3 <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> aside per person, then chop the<strong> remaining lettuce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1721380157681-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1721380157681-x400.jpg",
