            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1721119100111-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1721119100111-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, divide the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> and <strong>slaw</strong> between the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Top each tortilla with the<strong> crispy fish</strong> and a generous drizzle of the <strong>chipotle hot honey </strong>– these are your <strong>baja-style fish tacos with chipotle hot honey</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced chillies </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
